crimson: crimson (a game of strategy)
crimson:
crimson: Crimson Fields is a turn-based tactical war game. It can be played
crimson: against a human opponent in hot-seat mode in front of the same
crimson: machine, over a network, or via e-mail, or against the computer.
crimson: The game comes with tools for creating custom maps and campaigns,
crimson: and a converter for maps from the classic games Battle Isle and
crimson: History Line.
crimson:
crimson: homepage:  http://crimson.seul.org/
